			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When utilizing the dataset for life cycle assessment, it is crucial to consider the geographical relevance and technological representativeness of the data with regard to China's average copper production as opposed to a specific enterprise. The studied period spans from 2010 to 2050, reflecting projections in copper demand. Ensure that the scope of your assessment aligns with the functional unit of 1 kg copper. Employ the life cycle environmental impacts conducted with the CMLCA 6.0 software and the CML2001 impact categories for consistency in evaluation.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用数据集进行生命周期评估时，必须考虑数据的地理相关性和技术代表性，这些数据代表的是中国平均铜生产情况而非特定企业。研究期间从2010年到2050年，反映了铜需求的预测。确保您的评估范围与1公斤铜的功能单位一致。为了评估的一致性，请使用CMLCA 6.0软件和CML2001影响类别进行的生命周期环境影响分析。</useAdviceForDataSet>
